Duncan's death in June left the Tennessee seat vacant. The New York
seat is vacant after the resignation of Mario Biaggi.
   The trend line gives the anticipated new party division for the
U.S. House. It is calculated by adding the number of races which
each party has won or is leading.
</TEXT>
