<TEXT>
   Marilyn Quayle says the campaign so far
``hasn't been a picnic'' because of persistent questions about the
background of her husband, vice presidential nominee Dan Quayle.
   But, she said, ``when you have the truth on your side, things
aren't near as trying as they would be.''
